@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #f8f8f8
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor<<active>> #e6ffe6
  BorderColor<<active>> #00b300
  FontColor<<active>> #004d00
}

[*] --> Idle

state Idle {
  [*] --> WaitingForInput
}

WaitingForInput --> Processing   : user clicks "Start"\nor timer expires
WaitingForInput --> Error        : invalid input

Processing --> WaitingForInput   : task completed
Processing --> Saving            : auto-save triggered
Processing --> Error             : exception thrown

Saving --> WaitingForInput       : save successful
Saving --> Error                 : save failed

Error --> WaitingForInput        : user acknowledges
Error --> [*]                    : timeout (3×)

WaitingForInput -[hidden]> Processing
Processing -[hidden]> Saving
Saving -[hidden]> Error
@enduml